data.description: Great doublewide setting on a quiet picturesque dead-end street. This home has 3 bedroom 2 bath with 1296 sq feet to enjoy. The home has trees lining the property with no neighbors behind you. With the large kitchen opens to dining room and on into the large living room  Stainless steel appliances stove, refrigerator plus microwave, dishwasher plus the hardwood floors round out the kitchen. There is a wood stove to warm up the home this fall. With porches on front, side and back of property you can enjoy the outdoor living on this one acre or just watch the children  play on the Playset under the beautiful shaded tree. Two large sheds to store outdoor equipment.  Schedule your personal showing today!Just minutes from Walmart.
